{"tid":1754234,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"地區工作check list","createTime":"2019-11-25T06:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T06:51:40.000Z","uid":161603,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"885a1c1e5e3cf3ece8d7a4a6e94d18f0705bc5d2","tid":1754234,"uid":161603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:47:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>而家先係開始，請做好你地份工！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">實質工作</span></span></strong><br />\n出席90%以上區議會會議<br />\n各項成功爭取（小至巴士線，修理設施道路，大至社會議題）<br />\n長期開放議員辦事處(協助填表申請政府資助etc.)<br />\n每星期最小各一次早晚街站匯報工作<br />\n於地區fb經常爆光！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">地區活動&mdash;每季1-2次</span></strong><br />\n老人探訪！！<br />\n量血壓<br />\n剪頭髮<br />\n平價義賣(柴米油鹽etc.)<br />\n本地遊(離島，米埔etc.)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">地區活動&mdash;每年1-2次</span></strong><br />\n打疫苗<br />\n影證件相<br />\n(離港旅遊團）<br />\n蛇齋餅<br />\n寫揮春<br />\n<br />\n請每日笑面迎人，明知係藍絲都要，你係代表緊我地區嘅後生仔女。你可以有性格，但吾好忘記全區人都有份出糧俾你，係你嘅客仔<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">月入三皮半吾係咁易拎的！高過d曱甴</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n利申，居住於民主派得票數頭十，上屆踢走保皇今年成功連仼的社區。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎再加"},{"pid":"1f748d533331d72957f3bfbb87941cec8f08936a","tid":1754234,"uid":161603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:48:06.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"abec1a0c83e2086e9e00ba4b650ce75ac15a99cb","tid":1754234,"uid":161603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:48:39.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"49ab00570273fb0cb5d3e9f128c684d70f7b693a","tid":1754234,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:48:59.000Z","msg":"（twitter戰線)國際都關注今次香港的區選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitte